{"word":"G4998 - σώφρων - sṓphrōn - so'-frone - Discreet","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σώφρων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sṓphrōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">so'-frone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Discreet</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தெளிந்த புத்தியுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. of sound mind, sane"},{"paragraph":"2. curbing one's desires and impulses, self - controlled, temperate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G4982 - σώζω - sṓzō - sode'-zo/4982\">G4982</a> and that of <a href=\"#/G5424 - φρήν - phrḗn - frane/5424\">G5424</a>; <i>safe</i> (<i>sound</i>) in <i>mind</i>, that is, <i>self controlled</i> (<i>moderate</i> as to opinion or passion): - discreet, sober, temperate.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4993/4993\">G4993</a>, <a href=\"#/G4994/4994\">G4994</a>, <a href=\"#/G4995/4995\">G4995</a>, <a href=\"#/G4996/4996\">G4996</a>, <a href=\"#/G4997/4997\">G4997</a>, <a href=\"#/G4998/4998\">G4998</a>"}]}